{"id":["109245299277521945"],"username":["ccav"],"acct":["ccav"],"display_name":["維尼之聲"],"locked":[false],"bot":[false],"discoverable":[true],"indexable":[false],"group":[false],"created_at":["2022-10-28T00:00:00.000Z"],"note":["<p>史记：<br />赵国末年维尼专权，宦官走狗横行，狼狈为奸。<br />对外谄媚对内专横，打压异己秘密抓捕，<br />焚书坑儒闭目塞听，操纵言论愚弄大众，<br />遮掩罪孽粉饰太平，<br />视万民如刍狗、待百姓以牛羊，<br />罪大莫及罄竹难书！<br />下民无知人云亦云，以黑为白认贼作父，<br />何其哀哉！<br />是曰：<br />无耻是卑劣者的通行证，<br />无脑是鱼肉们的墓志铭。<\/p><p>有诗为证：<br />万马齐喑究可哀，一窝鼠蚁竞横行。<br />搬是弄非祸自生，搞风搅雨史留名。<br />焚书坑儒何足道，闭耳塞嘴愧天恩。<br />三年灾害四千万，瞠目结舌谢神明。<br />天不生我长如夜，毛病不改积恶习。<br />古来草熊逊颜色，抓人禁评显威仪。<br />满脸喷粪谁任性，通商宽衣我妄为。<br />寡廉鲜耻立牌坊，倒行逆施新罗衣。<br />民若有魂魂自哀，才脱苦海苦又来。<br />韭菜犹能望春归，沦落为羊任割㱰。<br />病久入深麻不仁，烹酒饮乐今何夕。<br />长夜难明夜复深，寥若晨星星安在！<\/p><p>----「一本歪经•庚子年清明祭」<\/p>"],"url":["https://mastodon.social/@ccav"],"uri":["https://mastodon.social/users/ccav"],"avatar":["https://files.mastodon.social/accounts/avatars/109/245/299/277/521/945/original/42b3db6d442133be.png"],"avatar_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/accounts/avatars/109/245/299/277/521/945/original/42b3db6d442133be.png"],"header":["https://files.mastodon.social/accounts/headers/109/245/299/277/521/945/original/84dfa2f731ed94d5.jpeg"],"header_static":["https://files.mastodon.social/accounts/headers/109/245/299/277/521/945/original/84dfa2f731ed94d5.jpeg"],"followers_count":[1409],"following_count":[18],"statuses_count":[3238],"last_status_at":["2024-10-06"],"hide_collections":[true],"noindex":[true],"emojis":[],"roles":[],"fields":[{"name":["Telegram投稿"],"value":["<a href=\"https://t.me/+0IJmt0SxBUk1YjVh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer me\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://<\/span><span class=\"\">t.me/+0IJmt0SxBUk1YjVh<\/span><span class=\"invisible\"><\/span><\/a>"],"verified_at":{}},{"name":["Matrix投稿"],"value":["<a href=\"https://matrix.to/#/!gGfdwUAUACYRFEITTf:matrix.org?via=matrix.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer me\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https